                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "New CJK UI fonts introduced on Vista  and  (most) CJK outline fonts on Linux look nicer with anti-aliasing on than XP CJK fonts  with bitmap glyphs. ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Well, others may not agree (some Chinese linux users definitely  do not agree with me :-))\n", 
